        SO_ANYWAY_AS_I_WAS_SAYING                                              = 6778,  -- (So anyway, as I was saying...)
        WELCOME_TO_DO_YOU_WISH_TO_CHANGE_YOUR                                  = 6779,  -- Welcome to [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst]. Do you wish to change your allegiance from your current one to [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst]?
        ASK_ABOUT_CHANGING_YOUR_ALLEGIANCE_YES_NO                              = 6780,  -- Ask about changing your allegiance? Yes. No.
        THEN_GOOD_JOURNEY_SIR_MISS                                             = 6781,  -- Then, good journey, sir/miss].
        YOU_CAN_APPLY_HERE_TO_CHANGE_YOUR_ALLEGIANCE                           = 6782,  -- You can apply here to change your allegiance to [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst].
        WE_WILL_HAVE_TO_SEAL_AWAY_SOME_OF                                      = 6783,  -- We will have to seal away some of your memories as an international security measure. Those memories will be unsealed should you change your allegiance back to your former country.
        INCIDENTALLY_IF_THIS_IS_YOUR_FIRST_TIME_CHANGING                       = 6784,  -- Incidentally, if this is your first time changing your allegiance, you will have to start over from rank 1 in your new nation.
        YOUR_RANK_IN_YOUR_FORMER_NATION_IS_STILL                               = 6785,  -- Your rank in your former nation is still kept, so if you change your allegiance back you will return to your previous rank.
        IN_ADDITION_YOU_WILL_RETAIN_YOUR_CURRENT_CONQUEST                      = 6786,  -- In addition, you will retain your current conquest points as well as any records of your expeditionary force quests. Oh, and you will be required to pay a processing fee of # gil along with your application for transfer.
        YOU_WILL_ALSO_RETAIN_YOUR_CURRENT_RANK_IN                              = 6787,  -- You will also retain your current rank in [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst], which is presently rank #.
        IN_ADDITION_YOU_WILL_RETAIN_YOUR_CURRENT_CONQUEST_2                    = 6788,  -- In addition, you will retain your current conquest points as well as any records of your expeditionary force quests. Oh, and you will be required to pay a processing fee of # gil along with your application for transfer.
        DO_YOU_STILL_WISH_TO_CHANGE_YOUR_ALLEGIANCE                            = 6789,  -- Do you still wish to change your allegiance?
        CHANGE_YOUR_ALLEGIANCE_TO_YES_NO                                       = 6790,  -- Change your allegiance to [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst]? Yes. No.
        I_AM_OBLIGATED_TO_ASK_YOU_AGAIN_ARE                                    = 6791,  -- I am obligated to ask you again: Are you sure you want to go through with this?
        CHANGE_YOUR_ALLEGIANCE_TO_YES_NO_2                                     = 6792,  -- Change your allegiance to [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst]? Yes. No.
        I_KNOW_IT_ISN_T_AN_EASY_DECISION                                       = 6793,  -- I know it isn't an easy decision to make. Please think it through before you decide.
        VERY_WELL_I_WILL_ACCEPT_YOUR_APPLICATION_FOR                           = 6794,  -- Very well. I will accept your application for [San d'Orian/Bastokan/Windurstian] citizenship.
        I_WILL_NOW_CAST_A_SPELL_TO_SEAL                                        = 6795,  -- I will now cast a spell to seal some of your memories away. Close your eyes...
        MAY_YOUR_DECISION_BE_A_WISE_ONE                                        = 6796,  -- May your decision be a wise one...
        YOU_ARE_NOW_A_CITIZEN_OF                                               = 6797,  -- You are now a citizen of [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst]!
        THIS_IS_WHERE_CITIZENS_OF_OTHER_NATIONS_APPLY                          = 6798,  -- This is where citizens of other nations apply for citizenship in [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst]. Since you are [San d'Orian/Bastokan/Windurstian], there is not much I can do for you.
        I_CANNOT_ACCEPT_APPLICATIONS_FOR_CITIZENSHIP_WHILE_YOU                 = 6799,  -- I cannot accept applications for [San d'Orian/Bastokan/Windurstian] citizenship while you are on a mission.
        YOUR_HOME_COUNTRY_SEEMS_TO_BE_IN_TROUBLE                               = 6800,  -- Your home country seems to be in trouble... I cannot accept [San d'Orian/Bastokan/Windurstian] citizenship applications at this time.
        WELL_YOU_MUST_BE_NEW_HERE_WELCOME_TO                                   = 6801,  -- Well, you must be new here. Welcome to Bastok's renowned Blacksmiths' Guild. We're a union for steelworkers, gunsmiths, armor-workers, and the like.
        WHAT_DO_YOU_MEAN_YOU_DON_T_WANT                                        = 6802,  -- What do you mean, you don't want to join? You're missing your chance to be trained by the best!
        SO_YOU_RE_LOOKING_FOR_A_LITTLE_WORK                                    = 6803,  -- So you're looking for a little work to do alongside your adventuring? Well, don't take this job lightly, or you may just get burned!
        MAYBE_WE_SHOULD_START_YOU_OFF_WITH_CRYSTAL                             = 6804,  -- Maybe we should start you off with crystal synthesis. You know what a crystal is by now, don't you? Well, those crystals are packed full of power that's just waiting to be unleashed. The process of crystal synthesis utilizes that power for craftwork.
        A_CRYSTAL_RECEIVES_AN_IMAGE_FROM_THE_USER                              = 6805,  -- A crystal receives an image from the user, and uses that image to transform matter. In other words, the more refined the mind, the better the product.
        DID_YOU_GET_ALL_THAT_I_DON_T                                           = 6806,  -- Did you get all that? I don't expect you to become a master in a few days, so don't feel that there's a need to rush into things, but you know what they say--learn by doing.
        IF_YOU_WANT_TO_KNOW_MORE_JUST_ASK                                      = 6807,  -- If you want to know more, just ask the smiths here in the guild. They're a little difficult at first, but once you get to know them, they rub off on you.
        THE_ROAD_TO_BECOMING_A_MASTER_BLACKSMITH_DOESN                         = 6808,  -- The road to becoming a master blacksmith doesn't end in this room. Keep your eyes open for tricks from other trades that might assist you in your journey.
        GO_FORTH_AND_BE_PROUD_OF_YOUR_BLACKSMITHING                            = 6809,  -- Go forth and be proud of your blacksmithing ability. But remember that your journey does not end here. A true professional is well-versed in many areas. Good luck!
        YOU_SAY_YOU_RE_READY_TO_MOVE_UP                                        = 6810,  -- You say you're ready to move up in the guild? Well, let's see what you can do. Make me %.
        IF_I_LIKE_IT_I_LL_TEACH_YOU                                            = 6811,  -- If I like it, I'll teach you some new techniques.
        NOT_BAD_NOT_GOOD_BUT_NOT_BAD_FROM                                      = 6812,  -- ... Not bad. Not good, but not bad. From now on your blacksmith title will be [amateur/recruit/initiate/novice/apprentice]. Keep up the good work, rookie.
        HMM_I_SEE_THAT_YOU_RE_STARTING_TO                                      = 6813,  -- Hmm... I see that you're starting to get the hang of this. From now on, your blacksmith title will be journeyman! I look forward to seeing your next work.
        EXCELLENT_I_SEE_THAT_YOU_ARE_FINALLY_STARTING                          = 6814,  -- ... Excellent! I see that you are finally starting to make a name for yourself. From now on, your blacksmith title will be artisan! That's quite some talent you have!
        THERE_IS_NOTHING_MORE_I_CAN_TEACH_YOU                                  = 6815,  -- ... There is nothing more I can teach you. From today on, I am honored to call you an adept, my rival...and my friend!
