        YOUR_WING_SKILL_IMPROVED_TO                                            = 8127,  -- Your wing skill improved to #!
        HEY_YOU_RE_AN_ADVENTURER_AREN_T_YOU                                    = 8128,  -- Hey, you're an adventurer, aren't you? I have this idea... I was thinking of providing tours of the surrounding areas to fledgling adventurers.
        YOU_KNOW_IF_YOU_SHOW_THEM_REALLY_INTERESTING                           = 8129,  -- You know, if you show them really interesting sights, it'd make them want to go out and see more, right?
        OF_COURSE_IT_WON_T_BE_FREE_ONCE                                        = 8130,  -- Of course, it won't be free once it gets going, but for now, I'm looking for volunteers to try it out and tell me what they think! No charge!
        YOU_WANNA_TRY_YOU_LL_HAVE_TO_BE                                        = 8131,  -- You wanna try? You'll have to be in a party where all members are level fifteen or less.
        MY_PARTNER_HUNTING_BEAR_IS_WAITING_NEAR_DRACHENFALL                    = 8132,  -- My partner, Hunting Bear, is waiting near Drachenfall in North Gustaberg. It's on the road that goes from North Gustaberg to Konschtat.
