        ADVENTURER_I_NEED_TO_HAVE_A_WORD_WITH                                  = 9081,  -- Adventurer, I need to have a word with you. Could you come to the Northern Cannonry?
        I_APOLOGIZE_FOR_ALL_THE_MYSTERY                                        = 9082,  -- I apologize for all the mystery...
        BUT_I_NEEDED_TO_SPEAK_WITH_YOU_IN                                      = 9083,  -- ...but I needed to speak with you in private.
        YOU_SEE                                                                = 9084,  -- You see...
        I_HAVE_A_REQUEST_FOR_YOU_FROM_A                                        = 9085,  -- I have a request for you from a senator.
        HE_CLAIMS_TO_HAVE_BEEN_RECEIVING_THREATS                               = 9086,  -- He claims to have been receiving threats.
        EVERY_DAY_THERE_HAVE_BEEN_MOUNTAINS_OF_INCOHERENT                      = 9087,  -- Every day there have been mountains of incoherent, slanderous letters arriving at the President's Office. So many, in fact, the herald delivering these threats, rather than the senator himself, has collapsed from the strain.
        NOW_WE_HAVE_NAJI_DELIVERING_THE_MAIL_IF                                = 9088,  -- Now we have Naji delivering the mail, if you can imagine it.
        THIS_INTERRUPTION_TO_OUR_DUTIES_NOT_TO_MENTION                         = 9089,  -- This interruption to our duties, not to mention Naji's complaining, has become intolerable. So I did some investigating. From the letters, I was able to discover the identity of the writer and negotiate a meeting at the Tenshodo here in Bastok. However...
        THERE_IS_ONE_SMALL_PROBLEM_THE_LETTER_WRITER                           = 9090,  -- There is one small problem. The letter writer won't meet with anyone unless they bring a certain diary.
        THIS_DIARY_IS_SUPPOSEDLY_HIDDEN_SOMEWHERE_WITHIN_THE                   = 9091,  -- This diary is supposedly hidden somewhere within the Palborough Mines. I have no idea why it would be there.
        THE_MYTHRIL_MUSKETEERS_ARE_FAR_TOO_BUSY_WITH                           = 9092,  -- The Mythril Musketeers are far too busy with more pressing matters to conduct a search of the mines, and we certainly can't expect the senator to go in our stead.
        THIS_IS_WHERE_YOU_COME_IN_WOULD_YOU                                    = 9093,  -- This is where you come in. Would you be willing to take this task upon yourself?
        WILL_YOU_PERFORM_THIS_TASK_SURE_THE_MINES                              = 9094,  -- Will you perform this task? Sure, the mines are like my second home. I also have more pressing matters...
