        THIS_IS_NOT_ONLY_ABOUT_THE_DIARY_YOU                                   = 9096,  -- This is not only about the diary. You will also be required to eliminate the letter writer. I am sure your skills in combat will be tested before this matter has been put to rest.
        SHOW_THE_DIARY_TO_KAGETORA_AND_HE_WILL                                 = 9097,  -- Show the diary to Kagetora, and he will tell you where the author of these threatening letters can be found. I leave the negotiations to your discretion.
        AH_YES_PLEASE_DO_NOT_MENTION_ANY_OF                                    = 9098,  -- Ah, yes. Please do not mention any of this to Romualdo.
        SENATOR_ALOIS_HAS_HIS_SUSPICIONS                                       = 9099,  -- Senator Alois has his suspicions.
        APPARENTLY_ROMUALDO_HAS_BEEN_SEEN_IN_THE_COMPANY                       = 9100,  -- Apparently Romualdo has been seen in the company of some strange character as of late.
        BUT_PUTTING_ASIDE_THESE_SPECULATIONS_THERE_IS_REASON                   = 9101,  -- But putting aside these speculations, there is reason to believe that someone has been providing the letter writer with information.
        IT_IS_UNLIKELY_THAT_THE_WRITER_IS_IN                                   = 9102,  -- It is unlikely that the writer is in direct contact with an employee of the President's Office, so I assume there must be a messenger of some sort.
        I_WANT_YOU_TO_FIND_OUT_THE_IDENTITY                                    = 9103,  -- I want you to find out the identity of this messenger as well.
        VIRESEFILANT_WHAT_IS_GOING_ON_HERE_I_MUST                              = 9104,  -- Viresefilant...? What is going on here? I must speak with Senator Alois...
        WHAT_BUSINESS_DOES_AN_ADVENTURER_HAVE_WITH_ME                          = 9105,  -- What business does an adventurer have with me?
        IS_THAT_SO_HOW_STRANGE_I_HAVE_NO                                       = 9106,  -- Is that so? How strange, I have no memory of making any such request. The next time you see Ayame, you tell her to keep my name out of her affairs.
        SENATOR_ALOIS_FORGIVE_THIS_INTERRUPTION_BUT_THERE_IS                   = 9107,  -- Senator Alois, forgive this interruption, but there is something I need to spe--
        CAN_T_I_GET_ANY_PEACE_AROUND_HERE                                      = 9108,  -- Can't I get any peace around here?
        PLEASE_EXPLAIN_TO_ME_ABOUT_THIS_NEW_ASSASSIN                           = 9109,  -- Please explain to me about this new assassin group.
        ASSASSA_WHATSITS_WHAT_IN_VANA_DIEL_ARE_YOU                             = 9110,  -- Assassa-whatsits? What in Vana'diel are you babbling about?
        SAVE_THE_ACT_SENATOR_KAGETORA_OF_THE_TENSHODO                          = 9111,  -- Save the act, Senator. Kagetora of the Tenshodo told me everything.
        CREATING_THIS_FICTITIOUS_ASSASSIN_ORGANIZATION_TO_LURE_ADVENTURERS     = 9112,  -- Creating this fictitious assassin organization to lure adventurers into doing your dirty work is an abuse of power.
        I_DID_NO_SUCH_THING_I_JUST_MENTIONED                                   = 9113,  -- I did no such thing. I just mentioned the rumor that an assassin group might exist. It's not my fault if they took things the wrong way.
        WHAT_ARE_YOU_TRYING_TO_SAY_EXACTLY_THAT                                = 9114,  -- What are you trying to say exactly? That I have to take responsibility for other people's misunderstandings now, hmmm?
        I_AM_ALREADY_IN_A_POSITION_OF_RESPONSIBILITY                           = 9115,  -- I am already in a position of responsibility.
        I_HAVE_ELIMINATED_THE_OBJECTIVE_AS_PER_YOUR                            = 9116,  -- I have eliminated the objective as per your orders, Senator.
        ID_9117                                                                = 9117,  -- ...!!!
        AH_GOOD_WORK_GOOD_WORK_YOU_HAVE_CARRIED                                = 9118,  -- Ah! Good work, good work. You have carried out my request to shut up that big-mou...I mean, remove that menace to our nation most admirably.
        FROM_NOW_ON_PLEASE_INFORM_ME_IN_ADVANCE                                = 9119,  -- From now on, please inform me in advance when you intend to make a report.
