        THERE_MUST_BE_SOME_SORT_OF_MISTAKE                                     = 9121,  -- There must be some sort of mistake.
        I_DON_T_KNOW_ANYTHING_ABOUT_ANY_ASSASSINS                              = 9122,  -- I don't know anything about any assassins.
        WHAT_MAKES_YOU_THINK_THAT_I_WOULD_BE                                   = 9123,  -- What makes you think that I would be able to authorize something like that in the first place? I believe you've taken some of my previous comments in entirely the wrong light. In the future, pay a little more attention to the details.
        AND_DID_YOU_FIND_OUT_WHO_THE_MESSENGER                                 = 9124,  -- And did you find out who the messenger was? I specifically ordered you to discover who was running the information back and forth.
