        IF_YOU_HAVE_ANY_COMPLAINTS_KINDLY_MAKE_THEM                            = 9126,  -- If you have any complaints, kindly make them after you have brought me the messenger!
        SENATOR                                                                = 9127,  -- Senator!
        GUARDS_THERE_IS_AN_UNWELCOME_GUEST_IN_THE                              = 9128,  -- Guards! There is an unwelcome guest in the President's Office. Remove him immediately.
        ID_9129                                                                = 9129,  -- ...
        HONESTLY_THE_NUMBER_OF_ILL_MANNERED_HIRESWORDS_THESE                   = 9130,  -- Honestly, the number of ill-mannered hireswords these days just makes my head ache. Are you still here? Be on your way, adventurer.
        WHAT_IS_THE_MEANING_OF_THIS_SENATOR_THAT                               = 9131,  -- What is the meaning of this, Senator? That exchange appeared to be more than just a simple misunderstanding. You promised him a position as an assassin, didn't you?
        YOUR_ACTIONS_IN_THIS_MATTER_ARE_REPREHENSIBLE_YOU                      = 9132,  -- Your actions in this matter are reprehensible. You enlisted his services because of his exceptional skill, correct?
        THAT_LEVEL_OF_ABILITY_IS_NOT_SOMETHING_GAINED                          = 9133,  -- That level of ability is not something gained over a weekend training session. Do you have any idea of the sweat and tears one must go through to attain such perfection!?
        WHAT_IS_THAT_TO_ME                                                     = 9134,  -- What is that to me?
        WELL_I_KNOW_EXACTLY_WHAT_HE_HAS_GONE                                   = 9135,  -- Well, I know exactly what he has gone through. The toil and the blisters of constant practice. Swinging a katana until his arm was numb from the strain. Encouraging others to push on, even though he himself was ready to drop.
        EVEN_IF_I_DON_T_KNOW_EVERYTHING_ABOUT                                  = 9136,  -- Even if I don't know everything about him, I know that much. You will apologize for manipulating him and making a mockery of his effort.
        ID_9137                                                                = 9137,  -- ...
        SENATOR_2                                                              = 9138,  -- Senator...
        HUH                                                                    = 9139,  -- Huh...?
        I_VE_HAD_ABOUT_ENOUGH_OF_YOUR_LECTURING                                = 9140,  -- I've had about enough of your lecturing. If you're done whining, I'm sure you have other duties to attend to. Now get out!
        IF_THAT_IS_THE_WAY_IT_MUST_BE                                          = 9141,  -- If that is the way it must be. I'll take my leave.
        WOULD_YOU_ACCOMPANY_ME_PLEASE                                          = 9142,  -- %, would you accompany me, please?
        I_SUPPOSE_YOU_RE_THINKING_OF_CRYING_TO                                 = 9143,  -- I suppose you're thinking of crying to the president about this? What a pity he's far too busy to make time for the likes of you.
        I_AM_A_PATIENT_WOMAN                                                   = 9144,  -- I am a patient woman...
        GUARDS_THIS_ADVENTURER_IS_TO_BE_BANNED_FROM                            = 9145,  -- Guards! This adventurer is to be banned from entering the Metalworks, effective immediately!
        YOUR_METHODS_LACK_SUBTLETY                                             = 9146,  -- Your methods lack subtlety.
        WHO_ASKED_FOR_YOUR_OPINION_GET_OUT                                     = 9147,  -- Who asked for your opinion!? Get out!
