        WHO_IS_THIS_MAN                                                        = 9149,  -- Who is this man?
        THIS_IS_THE_MESSENGER_YOU_VE_BEEN_SEARCHING                            = 9150,  -- This is the messenger you've been searching for.
        PLEASE_FORGIVE_ME_I_WAS_THE_ONE_WHO                                    = 9151,  -- Please forgive me. I was the one who tricked Romualdo into revealing sensitive information about you, sir.
        SEEMS_HE_WAS_READY_TO_SELL_INFORMATION_TO                              = 9152,  -- Seems he was ready to sell information to other citizens who hold grudges against you as well. We were lucky this business was restricted to just one malcontent.
        UNBELIEVABLE_WELL_THEN_LAD_EXCELLENT_WORK_I_LL                         = 9153,  -- Unbelievable. Well then, lad, excellent work. I'll be able to sleep much easier tonight.
        THAT_S_THE_KIND_OF_EFFICIENCY_I_VE                                     = 9154,  -- That's the kind of efficiency I've come to expect from the Mythril Musketeers.
        ACTUALLY_IT_WASN_T_ME_WHO_CAUGHT_HIM                                   = 9155,  -- Actually, it wasn't me who caught him, sir. It was the man you ordered me to remove from the office a little while ago.
        SIR_YOU_DID_MENTION_YOU_WOULD_HEAR_WHAT                                = 9156,  -- Sir, you did mention you would hear what he had to say if he brought you the messenger. You really should listen to him.
        THE_THING_IS_THOUGH_HE_S_ALREADY_LEFT                                  = 9157,  -- The thing is, though, he's already left the Republic. Fed up with the treatment he's received, I'd imagine. So I'll do his talking for him.
        THERE_WAS_ONLY_ONE_THING_HE_WISHED_TO                                  = 9158,  -- There was only one thing he wished to say to you.
