        WHEN_YOUR_INVENTORY_IS_FULL_OR_YOU_CANNOT                              = 9424,  -- When your inventory is full, or you cannot carry any more of a certain item, the newly quarried item will be automatically discarded. If you wish, I can lend you one of these shovels, free of charge.
