        YOU_ARE_HERE_TO_REPORT_ON_YOUR_ACTIVITIES                              = 10135,  -- You are here to report on your activities, as well? The number of adventurers coming through here today has been nothing short of astounding. Now, about your report...
        PERHAPS_YOU_SHOULD_LEND_AN_EAR_TO_THE                                  = 10136,  -- Perhaps you should lend an ear to the townspeople a little more often. You might be surprised by the discoveries you can make by speaking with the local citizenry.
