        IT_APPEARS_YOU_SPEND_A_GREAT_DEAL_OF                                   = 10138,  -- It appears you spend a great deal of time interacting with the local citizenry. An admirable quality in an adventurer.
        AND_LET_S_SEE_HERE_DO_YOU_OFTEN                                        = 10139,  -- And, let's see here... Do you often avoid conversation with your adventuring companions? A time may come when you cannot achieve an adventuring goal on your own...
        AND_LET_S_SEE_HERE_YOU_SEEM_TO                                         = 10140,  -- And, let's see here... You seem to be participating in party conversation. Continue to communicate with your companions and you will reap the benefits that solid frienships bring.
        AND_LET_S_SEE_HERE_YOUR_LIVELY_PARTICIPATION                           = 10141,  -- And, let's see here... Your lively participation in party conversation must greatly enhance your adventuring activities. There is no greater asset to an adventurer than trustworthy companions.
