        IT_S_ABOUT_TIME_YOU_SHOWED_UP_THOUGHT                                  = 10145,  -- It's about time you showed up, %. Thought I'd find you resting up at home after what happened, but you just can't stay put, can you?
        I_WAS_ALMOST_READY_TO_THROW_IN_THE                                     = 10146,  -- I was almost ready to throw in the apron. Even the messengers I sent after you never got back to me...
        I_UNDERSTAND_THAT_YOU_RE_BUSY_WITH_MISSIONS                            = 10147,  -- %. I understand that you're busy with missions, but I had a hell of a time trying to get in touch with you.
        ANYWAY_AT_LEAST_YOU_RE_HERE_IN_TIME                                    = 10148,  -- Anyway, at least you're here in time to see off Tenzen.
        EVERYONE_ELSE_HAS_SAID_THEIR_GOODBYES_EXCEPT_YOU                       = 10149,  -- Everyone else has said their goodbyes except you, it seems.
