        WOULD_THAT_WE_COULD_DO_MORE_BUT_WE                                     = 11011,  -- Would that we could do more, but we are currently engaged with matters relevant to Bastok's national security. I would ask you to aid [us/your home nation] in the struggle against the Beastman Confederate first.
