        YOU_WILL_THAT_ALONE_PROVES_YOU_FEEL_A                                  = 11018,  -- You will? That alone proves you feel a strong bond between us.
        WELL_AT_THE_VERY_LEAST_I_FEEL_A                                        = 11019,  -- Well, at the very least, I feel a strong bond with you. How could I not, after you vanquished the Shadow Lord in Castle Zvahl?
