        WHAT_S_MORE_AFTERWARD_YOU_FOUND_WHAT_LAY                               = 11023,  -- What's more, afterward you found what lay deep within the recesses of despair and hatred. I found myself with nothing but the utmost respect for you.
        THERE_WAS_ALSO_THE_TIME_WHEN_I_CONFRONTED                              = 11024,  -- There was also the time when I confronted Zeid...no, my own past in Xarcabard.
