        MUTTER_HMM_HMM_GRUMBLE_TRUST                                           = 11076,  -- <Mutter> Hmm, hmm... <Grumble>...trust...
        WELL_I_CERTAINLY_DO_TRUST_YOU_AFTER_YOU                                = 11077,  -- Well, I certainly do trust you, after you led the incident with Volker and Zeid to a satisfactory conclusion.
        YOU_BROUGHT_TOGETHER_THE_MYTHRIL_MUSKETEERS_SO_THAT                    = 11078,  -- You brought together the Mythril Musketeers so that we could continue to protect Bastok and ensure the prosperity of her citizens.
        WHEN_I_THINK_ABOUT_FRIENDSHIP_I_AM_REMINDED                            = 11079,  -- When I think about friendship, I am reminded of my master, Werei.
        YOU_WERE_INSTRUMENTAL_IN_MY_MASTERY_OVER_THE                           = 11080,  -- You were instrumental in my mastery over the way of the axe. To find your calling, you must first think long and hard.
        AND_YOU_SHINED_A_BEAMING_RAY_OF_HOPE                                   = 11081,  -- And you shined a beaming ray of hope on those Galka grieving over the loss of their homeland.
        THE_BONDS_OF_BROTHERHOOD_ARE_A_THING_TO                                = 11082,  -- The bonds of brotherhood are a thing to treasure--and for those Galka grieving over the loss of their homeland--to reclaim.
        IT_WAS_THANKS_TO_YOUR_EFFORTS_THAT_WE                                  = 11083,  -- It was thanks to your efforts that we found the piece of wood Werei left behind[, wasn't it?/.]
        THAT_SIMPLE_FRAGMENT_TOGETHER_WITH_THE_WISE_WORDS                      = 11084,  -- That simple fragment, together with the wise words of Gumbah, changed the very future of the Galka race.
        MY_CALLING_NOW_IS_TO_ENSURE_THAT_GALKA                                 = 11085,  -- My calling now is to ensure that Galka of all stripes learn to celebrate their pasts, treasure those around them, and love Bastok as if it were their own.
        WHEN_I_RUMINATE_UPON_FRIENDSHIP_ONE_EPISODE_IN                         = 11086,  -- When I ruminate upon friendship, one episode in particular comes to mind: when you helped me renew my ties with Raogrimm and Deidogg.
        I_WAS_A_CHILD_I_MAY_HAVE_CHOSEN                                        = 11087,  -- [Ah, friendship. When/Further, when] I was a child, I may have chosen to become an adventurer myself should I have met one as passionate as you.
        OF_COURSE_IT_WAS_MY_DEEP_ADMIRATION_FOR                                = 11088,  -- Of course, it was my deep admiration for Raogrimm that ended up leading me to the Mythril Musketeers.
